Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Worked compositions", "Section",
 CellID->203,ExpressionUUID->"4c78ae85-a557-4b07-8353-54f8a6b6f647"],

Cell["\<\
The graph captures two structurally distinct kinds of composition. We walk \
through one example of each, then show a property-dispatch case that the \
graph deliberately does not record.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"26d12cb7-2710-4455-bbc2-c56488df0b24"],

