Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
The paclet-wide flow view. Operator-like heads (green) cluster in the upper \
rows with self-loops indicating they preserve their target type; Transforms \
(yellow) sit one layer below; Distance / Predicate / Similarity (purple / \
red) are pure sinks with only incoming arrows:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"5ecde46a-a9d5-4b76-99ca-e03e7be082bd"],

